{"tid":312822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE生擇業 愛教育心理學不愛會計機械工程 酒店旅遊最受歡迎科目","createTime":"2017-07-07T18:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T09:50:45.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e95bf4569b09f4e28fd690058fbee649e4c5cefc","tid":312822,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:56:33.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】今年中學文憑試（DSE）將於下周三（12日）放榜，其後考生便可修改大學聯招的選科次序，有機構調查發現近七成三應屆考生有意升讀大學，而酒店及旅遊管理學科更連續4年成為最受歡迎主修學科。至於未來職業，應屆文憑試考生最希望將來投身教育行業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n欲當公僕者減<br />\n<br />\n優才資源中心有限公司於去年11月至今年1月，以不記名問卷方式，訪問了3092名來自35間不同地區學校的應屆中學文憑試考生，了解其選科和就業意向。<br />\n<br />\n調查發現，考生選科時會考慮文憑試成績及對學科的興趣，而最受歡迎的學科為酒店及旅遊管理，其次為心理學和護理學，與去年排名相同；統計及精算學系則成為最不受歡迎的科目，其次是機械/電機工程及歷史。<br />\n<br />\n近兩成稱沒能力處理學業問題<br />\n<br />\n調查亦顯示，考生選擇未來工作首要考慮個人興趣及性格，其次是個人能力。<br />\n<br />\n最受歡迎行業首3位分別是教育、醫療服務/製藥及酒店/旅遊，而有興趣任政府公務員的考生亦減少，從2014年受歡迎的第二位（25.5%），一直下降至今年的第六位（18.0%）；最不受歡迎的行業是會計/審計，其次是保險及法律，其中不想從事法律行業的人數亦增加，由2014年的15.1%上升至今年的18.1%。<br />\n<br />\n優才資源中心總監陳偉權表示，商界應多給鼓勵，例如舉辦工作影子計劃，讓學生了解各行各業的工作，從而選擇適合自己的行業。<br />\n<br />\n問卷亦調查應屆文憑試考生處理逆境的能力，結果顯示，逾六成考生認為自己有責任處理與學業相關的問題，惟近兩成考生認為自己沒足夠能力處理問題，而學校組別（Banding）愈高的考生，則有愈大信心和責任感去處理自己的問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170707/s00011/1499363998507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170707%2Fs00011%2F1499363998507&d=xWuwrdy%2BTp%2FhwWFpPqP6CYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cfe55a12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170707%2Fs00011%2F1499363998507&h=04ee51fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170707/s00011/1499363998507</a> <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/025606_7865a08890b516e273e160b6bfc0f85e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F025606_7865a08890b516e273e160b6bfc0f85e.jpg&h=58ce2c86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乞食科目萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c8b991d75b15d7742c27bb4b39d618addab6ab","tid":312822,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:59:41.000Z","msg":"IT<br />\nEngine<br />\n被列為不受歡迎工作及科目之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af10597fa9e93d402ac39272125cc3c1a995b410","tid":312822,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:26:16.000Z","msg":"點解咁多人讀酒店"},{"pid":"120aa0904f2a33fff8e34a0e88d4511b15a5b87f","tid":312822,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6133eb41b609b2ec0a49ddedc7099b9cf0dee79d","tid":312822,"uid":39796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:27:23.000Z","msg":"心理學讀完乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c385396f97a6d15965572f9e304082112da95d","tid":312822,"uid":107755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"account狗都唔讀<br />\n三年一個course就同你一樣<br />\n做又辛苦，錢又小"},{"pid":"9ecf85b0b68308bf3d7716448190ab727f73f951","tid":312822,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於醒覺喇後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4346a238d990215df4d99353e66e5121dde33050","tid":312822,"uid":342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心理學讀完乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日都有人咁講<br />\n但又長期有人入<br />\n冇計啦 興趣嘅野"},{"pid":"8d8c5be1a310c47ebb9daf813868effcb4f67735","tid":312822,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於醒覺喇後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遲D 都變一國一制，讀法律把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b194702251f944dd5fd4b949118cda714a7beeec","tid":312822,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:40:04.000Z","msg":"而家話討厭會計，到final year咪一樣大把人apply Big4 &amp; 2nd tier。"},{"pid":"a59e9bb01f62e03f01b4226d6dc26f51a8e20a0e","tid":312822,"uid":123524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:50:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家話討厭會計，到final year咪一樣大把人apply Big4 &amp; 2nd tier。</blockquote><br />\n就是知 big4 唔只係請會計 grad 先取三大棄會計<br />\n最少三大個名考政府工 MT 有優勢<br />\n讀理大城大會計又入唔到 big4 個D正 on9"}]}